team 18 = Finding way to implement the clearScreen() function using C++
        An equivalent clearScreen() function with C++ can be as follows:

        void clearScreen() {
            #ifdef __linux__ 
                // if OS is linux-based
                system("clear");
            #elif _WIN64 || _WIN32 || __WINDOWS__
                // if OS is windows-based
                system("cls");
            #else
            #endif
        }

